detail.name: Vegeta (Mini) : DA
detail.effect:
[On Play] If your Leader is <Vegeta (Mini) : DA>, choose all Battle Cards in your opponent's Battle Area and reduce their costs by 3 for the turn.
[When Attacking] Choose up to 1 Battle Card in your opponent's Battle Area with a cost of 1 or less and place it at the bottom of its owner's deck.

detail.name: ベジータ(ミニ)：DA
detail.effect:
【登場時】自分のリーダーが「ベジータ(ミニ)：DA」の場合、相手のバトルエリアのバトルカードすべてを選び、このターン中、コスト-3。
【アタック時】相手のバトルエリアのコスト1以下のバトルカード1枚までを選び、デッキの下に置く。
